1
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,880
If you want to find the truth,

2
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:28,210
wouldn't it be easier to use the King of Zhenbei's power?

3
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:29,960
Besides, I don't think His Highness

4
00:01:29,960 --> 00:01:31,680
meant to keep it from you.

5
00:01:32,200 --> 00:01:33,479
He probably thought

6
00:01:33,479 --> 00:01:35,320
you never noticed.

7
00:01:36,039 --> 00:01:38,000
If you ask him properly,

8
00:01:38,600 --> 00:01:40,600
I'm sure he'll tell you.

9
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:42,200
If he were willing to tell me,

10
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:43,960
I wouldn't have run away from the wedding.

11
00:01:43,960 --> 00:01:45,880
I still think you should talk to the King of Zhenbei

12
00:01:45,880 --> 00:01:47,240
and clear the air.

13
00:01:48,160 --> 00:01:51,039
My gut tells me it's useless.

14
00:01:58,240 --> 00:01:59,800
It also tells me...

15
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,080
Ji Bai.

16
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,290
You're keeping something from me.

17
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:18,400
Right.

18
00:02:19,320 --> 00:02:21,200
You're actually quite honest.

19
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,640
That's in the future.

20
00:02:23,079 --> 00:02:25,800
It has nothing to do with the current you.

21
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,440
The current me...

22
00:02:28,720 --> 00:02:31,600
That doesn't mean it has nothing to do with the future me.

23
00:02:31,600 --> 00:02:33,200
We have a marriage contract.

24
00:02:35,720 --> 00:02:36,960
We do have a contract.

25
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:37,840
But...

26
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,280
I won't be bound by it.

27
00:02:40,880 --> 00:02:41,680
And?

28
00:02:43,120 --> 00:02:45,440
I made a promise to Jiujiu.

29
00:02:45,760 --> 00:02:48,160
To travel the world together when we grew up

30
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:50,579
and practice medicine to save lives.

31
00:02:52,320 --> 00:02:53,040
Even though

32
00:02:53,240 --> 00:02:55,240
he may no longer be able to fulfill

33
00:02:55,240 --> 00:02:56,800
our agreement,

34
00:02:57,079 --> 00:03:00,800
I will keep my own promise.

35
00:03:07,480 --> 00:03:08,720
If you marry me,

36
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:12,360
marriage won't hold us back.

37
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:15,920
I can travel the world with you.

38
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,840
You can practice medicine to save lives

39
00:03:18,840 --> 00:03:19,920
and help the world.

40
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,520
I'll protect you.

41
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,840
I...

42
00:03:37,000 --> 00:03:41,240
I should go check on Chuyun.

43
00:03:46,720 --> 00:03:47,800
You...

44
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:50,480
stripped off my clothes just now.

45
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,650
My innocence is ruined.

46
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,460
You have to take responsibility.

47
00:03:59,920 --> 00:04:01,920
You never change.

48
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:10,440
Is it because Duyu is the one you're looking for

49
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,160
that you're ignoring me?

50
00:04:17,279 --> 00:04:19,519
He is not the one I'm looking for.

51
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,579
On the contrary, I find

52
00:04:22,040 --> 00:04:24,400
Duyu and Chuyun quite strange.

53
00:04:24,880 --> 00:04:25,940
Why do you say that?

54
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,120
Chuyun said

55
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:32,880
her benefactor settled her in the wooden cabin.

56
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:37,120
But she doesn't know who that person is.

57
00:04:38,040 --> 00:04:40,040
This Duyu also hinted

58
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:43,240
that he lived in the wooden cabin for a long time.

59
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:44,650
Hey, think about it.

60
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,320
Everyone in town knows

61
00:04:46,320 --> 00:04:48,650
he is the Young Master of the medical hall.

62
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:51,060
If he really was the one who saved Chuyun,

63
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:52,720
then why did Chuyun say

64
00:04:53,200 --> 00:04:55,659
she didn't know the benefactor's identity?

65
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,640
Oh, forget it.

66
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,280
It's not important anyway.

67
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,340
On the contrary, I feel

68
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,680
that Duyu's constant hinting

69
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,560
is very strange.

70
00:05:07,440 --> 00:05:08,520
Besides,

71
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,920
I only mentioned my past with Jiujiu

72
00:05:11,960 --> 00:05:13,920
to Chuyun.

73
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:16,960
He has designs on you.

74
00:05:20,440 --> 00:05:22,680
Memorize the Treatise on Cold Damage when you have time.

75
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:26,480
Don't fill your head with these things.

76
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:29,280
Then can I stay?

77
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,680
I want to be by your side more.

78
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:36,800
Bad news!

79
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:38,880
Miss Chuyun,

80
00:05:38,880 --> 00:05:40,080
her condition has worsened.

81
00:05:40,080 --> 00:05:41,880
Doctor Ji, please go take a look.

82
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,480
Let's go.

83
00:05:47,400 --> 00:05:50,520
It seems something is blocking Miss Chuyun's chest.

84
00:05:50,720 --> 00:05:53,480
Since she has been bedridden for so long,

85
00:05:54,040 --> 00:05:55,480
she must have developed a blood clot.

86
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,940
I have tried many methods,

87
00:05:57,080 --> 00:05:58,760
but I still cannot remove it.

88
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:01,440
If this continues,

89
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,280
I fear it will block her meridians.

90
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:04,680
That would be dangerous.

91
00:06:04,760 --> 00:06:06,320
What should we do?

92
00:06:11,520 --> 00:06:12,320
Perhaps

93
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:15,000
we can open her chest to remove it.

94
00:06:15,840 --> 00:06:17,640
You mean using a knife

95
00:06:19,000 --> 00:06:21,000
to cut it out of her chest?

96
00:06:28,320 --> 00:06:30,200
It's still too dangerous.

97
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,720
Let's stick to conservative treatment.

98
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:34,250
I'll use acupuncture on her

99
00:06:34,720 --> 00:06:36,880
to try and clear her meridians.

100
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,400
We can't just keep dragging this out.

101
00:06:39,720 --> 00:06:41,120
What if her condition worsens?

102
00:06:41,120 --> 00:06:42,280
I know.

103
00:06:42,280 --> 00:06:44,409
But I can't gamble with Chuyun's life.

104
00:06:44,480 --> 00:06:46,320
Open-chest surgery is extremely risky.

105
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,520
One slip-up

106
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,680
could cost her life.

107
00:06:54,520 --> 00:06:55,320
Li'er,

108
00:06:55,600 --> 00:06:57,640
there is something you must do.

109
00:06:58,520 --> 00:07:00,920
Father, please give me your instructions.

110
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:02,560
Ji Bai...

111
00:07:03,000 --> 00:07:03,860
cannot remain.

112
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,800
Father,

113
00:07:05,960 --> 00:07:09,620
didn't you say to monitor the Heir and the Princess Consort first,

114
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,940
and hold off on taking action for now?

115
00:07:12,080 --> 00:07:13,360
Ji Bai has excellent medical skills.

116
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,280
From what I know,

117
00:07:14,280 --> 00:07:16,840
she has started researching how to neutralize the poison.

118
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:17,770
If she succeeds,

119
00:07:17,960 --> 00:07:20,480
our plans will be in vain.

120
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:22,720
Yes, Father.

121
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:24,450
I will find the right moment

122
00:07:24,560 --> 00:07:26,440
to deal with Ji Bai properly.

123
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:28,480
Good, Li'er.

124
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:30,560
I have always trusted you to get things done.

125
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:31,360
Remember,

126
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:33,000
do it cleanly.

127
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,680
Leave no trace.

128
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:36,200
Yes.

129
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:44,000
My grand plan is about to succeed.

130
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:47,880
We cannot afford any mistakes at a time like this.

131
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:51,800
Is there no other way?

132
00:07:54,640 --> 00:07:56,920
I'll study the medical texts carefully again

133
00:07:56,920 --> 00:07:59,040
to see if there are other treatments.

134
00:07:59,240 --> 00:08:02,040
I'll treat her with medicine and acupuncture

135
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,370
to hopefully slow the deterioration.

136
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:09,040
That is all we can do for now.

137
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:11,960
Thank you both for your trouble.

138
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:13,420
I'll take care of her here.

139
00:08:15,960 --> 00:08:16,960
Let's go.

140
00:08:32,880 --> 00:08:34,200
Damn it.

141
00:08:34,760 --> 00:08:36,440
These two are inseparable.

142
00:08:36,640 --> 00:08:38,600
I must find a way to get the Heir

143
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:40,130
away from the Heir Consort.

144
00:08:59,920 --> 00:09:00,920
Hey.

145
00:09:01,080 --> 00:09:02,080
I remember

146
00:09:02,560 --> 00:09:06,280
that herb is right over by the wooden house.

147
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,720
Where are you going?

148
00:09:12,080 --> 00:09:14,740
I'm going into the mountains to find some herbs.

149
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:16,440
Hey.

150
00:09:18,360 --> 00:09:19,560
I can go by myself.

151
00:09:19,880 --> 00:09:21,000
Before I return,

152
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:23,560
read this Treatise on Cold Damage Disorders first.

153
00:09:23,560 --> 00:09:24,690
Finish reciting it.

154
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,040
Shanghan Lun.

155
00:09:52,480 --> 00:09:54,040
Young Master Du.

156
00:09:57,840 --> 00:09:59,480
Why are you here?

157
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:02,500
Why aren't you at the clinic with Chuyun?

158
00:10:02,760 --> 00:10:03,480
I...

159
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:06,080
I came to gather some herbs.

160
00:10:06,640 --> 00:10:08,480
These herbs are for Chuyun's condition.

161
00:10:08,480 --> 00:10:10,280
They will speed up her recovery.

162
00:10:11,160 --> 00:10:11,960
Let me see.

163
00:10:13,960 --> 00:10:15,000
This herb

164
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:17,720
indeed helps with Chuyun's condition.

165
00:10:18,040 --> 00:10:20,480
But its medicinal properties are quite potent.

166
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:22,410
You still need to use it carefully.

167
00:10:23,520 --> 00:10:25,680
Don't worry, I will be very careful.

168
00:10:26,360 --> 00:10:28,120
However, why is this herb

169
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,320
so prone to being eaten by insects?

170
00:10:43,400 --> 00:10:44,640
No.

171
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:48,330
I need to read something to refresh myself first.

172
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:01,840
Miaojiang maiden,

173
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:06,320
skilled in using poison techniques.

174
00:11:08,560 --> 00:11:09,680
Accidentally lost control,

175
00:11:09,680 --> 00:11:12,680
letting poisonous insects enter her heart and lungs.

176
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,440
Didn't Ji Bai and Du Yu

177
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,800
treat Chu Yun this way before?

178
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:27,160
I'm not sure.

179
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:29,560
It was already like this when I found it.

180
00:11:48,800 --> 00:11:49,800
You again.

181
00:11:50,880 --> 00:11:52,040
Divine Physician Ji,

182
00:11:52,040 --> 00:11:53,360
we meet again.

183
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:55,480
Why do you keep opposing me?

184
00:11:55,760 --> 00:11:56,960
All you need to know is

185
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,720
that today is the day you die.

186
00:12:10,640 --> 00:12:12,440
You actually took a blade for her.

187
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:13,080
Good.

188
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:15,680
I'll kill you both today.

189
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:21,170
Don't you dare hurt her.

190
00:12:21,320 --> 00:12:22,580
You escaped last time.

191
00:12:22,840 --> 00:12:24,760
You won't get away this time.

192
00:12:43,320 --> 00:12:44,680
Are you okay?

193
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,120
I'm fine.

194
00:12:46,720 --> 00:12:48,320
It's just a wound.

195
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:50,960
But I left in a rush today.

196
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:52,780
I didn't bring my medical kit.

197
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:56,320
Golden Trauma Medicine.

198
00:12:56,680 --> 00:12:57,400
Miss Ji,

199
00:12:57,400 --> 00:12:58,680
my arm is injured.

200
00:12:58,680 --> 00:12:59,480
I'm afraid...

201
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:00,720
Let me do it.

202
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,040
Your apprentice is here.

203
00:13:05,040 --> 00:13:06,440
Why trouble you, Master?

204
00:13:06,960 --> 00:13:07,880
Brother Du,

205
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:10,340
let me apply the medicine for you.

206
00:13:27,560 --> 00:13:28,320
Xiang.

207
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,090
Chen, Luo, Deng,

208
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,000
Yiyinan,

209
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:45,280
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng,

210
00:13:44,360 --> 00:13:44,760
Xiaoxiaoxue, Que, Yiyi,

211
00:13:44,760 --> 00:13:45,560
Xiaoxiaoxue.

212
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:14,920
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

213
00:14:18,280 --> 00:14:19,010
Panxiulong.

214
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:19,280
Lyu.

215
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:19,280
Xiao Zhangmeng.

216
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:19,280
Panxiuchong.

217
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:19,960
Lyu, Sun, Zhang, Meng.

218
00:14:19,280 --> 00:14:19,960
Panxiulong.
